Definition: deciduous shrub of eastern North America whose leaves turn scarlet in autumn and having racemes of yellow flowers followed by ellipsoid glossy red berries
Synonyms: Berberis_canadensis, barberry, deciduous, shrub, of, eastern, North, America, whose, leaves, turn, scarlet, in, autumn, and, having, racemes, yellow, flowers, followed, by, ellipsoid, glossy, red, berries
Category: noun.plant
